'''Sometutuza yɛ afehyia Otwa afahyɛ''' a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Agozome a ɛwɔ keta, wɔ Frao Mantam no di wɔ Ghana. Wodi saa [[afahyɛ]] yi nnawɔtwe mienu bere a w’adi Hogbetsotso afahyɛ no akyi<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/keta-sometutuza-festival/</ref>. Wodi no wɔ memenada a ɛtɔ so miensa wɔ Bosome a ɛtɔ 11 no mu<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>https://touringghana.com/volta-region/</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔyɛ oyikyerɛ wɔ ntaadehyɛ mu ne asaw die wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Ahenfo ne wɔn asoafo nso bɔ dwa data. Ahenfo de nkyea kɔma wɔn manhene no ma wɔhyɛ no bɔ sɛ wɔtaa n’akyi. Wɔda Ewefoɔ kente ahorɔw adi wɔ afahyɛ no ase na ntoma afoforo a wɔde wɔn nsa anwene no nso da adi wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref name="slutchtours.com">https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref><ref>https://www.ghanawebsolutions.com/serve.php?id=560&d=Sometutuza-Festival</ref><ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ no de kae bere a, wotuu firii wɔn tenabea dedaw no mu<ref name="slutchtours.com"/>.

